{"tid":2142033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"端傳媒做緊五週年全站限時免費開放","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:21.000Z","uid":267791,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"abfbf2a94a6694a6246c35479df1d73a39ca0a0a","tid":2142033,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">係平時要比錢先有得睇嘅高汁媒體啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月3-7號，仲有一日半！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n推介呢篇，值得我地借鏡同認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">【被美國用完即棄的庫爾德人，還對西方國家有甚麼期待？】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「羅賈瓦的領導者清楚地知道美國和特朗普背叛了羅賈瓦，但是除了依賴西方國家，我們別無他法。」<br />\n<br />\n那麼，他們為何還要岀來遊行？散落於四個國家的庫爾德人的獨立運動又該何去何從？......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200806-international-kurds-london/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200806-international-kurds-london%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=873fa463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200806-international-kurds-london/</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n以下補充庫爾德人面對緊咩事，睇完會有種熟悉嘅感覺，尤其15：28分開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">「當一個地方危在旦夕時，有人選擇離開。<br />\n但係對於一班庫爾德斯坦人嘅嚟講呢，佢地大部份都選擇留係自己鐘愛嘅地方。<br />\n守係前線，去為呢個地方付出。<br />\n只係為左真係見到呢一個家有獨立同自由嘅一日。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果籽呢條片真係好高質<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fLjLzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fLjLzT</a>"},{"pid":"da29f113089582b940210fede1c922802146206f","tid":2142033,"uid":35194,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n端係香港僅餘無幾唔做標題黨、理性深入分析既媒體，afford到既話超值得課金"},{"pid":"cae100e3c4b967580d457281c4d32b9e4254c783","tid":2142033,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ff3e84d260dfdc1525cb0f0e6de47b2f1a2c3d","tid":2142033,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c17acf13f531d39e527474bdf6611f87b422444","tid":2142033,"uid":152944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"有課開 推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d677c79b1a242b8401ba5d84b23bf68981748a95","tid":2142033,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4ee6ef3f4ac10335c224a939afa9d417fe9858","tid":2142033,"uid":105958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"960bc555d975b51c4d80ee8e4fcfefee1b97db07","tid":2142033,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"高質華文傳媒<br />\n係有時勁多錯字同繁簡轉換問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a2074d885790369421b561a96eb43eb5bfd169","tid":2142033,"uid":136608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n高質傳媒"},{"pid":"20f4191cb9f711516463fa16ff136bbd0ffbf4b7","tid":2142033,"uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT